The paper deals with content-based image retrieval using deep supervised hashing techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel information-theoretic measure, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
